title: Shin'ai
text:
"" is the 19th <a href="Single%20%28music%29">single</a> by Japanese singer and <a href="voice%20actress">voice actress</a> <a href="Nana%20Mizuki">Nana Mizuki</a>, which was released on January 21, 2009, by <a href="King%20Records%20%28Japan%29">King Records</a> bearing the catalog number KICM-1270. <a href="Musical%20composition">composed</a>, <a href="Arrangement">arranged</a>, and produced by members of Elements Garden, Miki Watabe, Yōhei Sugita, Hibiki, Sayuri, and Nishi-ken. The single reached number 2 in Japan's <a href="Oricon">Oricon</a> weekly singles charts for the week of February 1, 2009.
